---
import LayoutPantry from '../../layouts/LayoutPantry.astro';
import GlassCard from '../../components/GlassCard.astro';
---

<LayoutPantry
  title="PantryBaby: Coming Soon | BabyBlocks"
  description="PantryBaby is coming soon from BabyBlocks: your grocery list and pantry memory. Track what you have, what's running low, and what you need. Get notified when it launches."
  canonical="/coming-soon/pantrybaby"
>
  <section class="coming-hero section">
    <div class="container">
      <div class="coming-inner">
        <div class="coming-copy">
          <div class="label-chip">Coming Soon</div>
          <h1>PantryBaby</h1>
          <p class="coming-tagline">Your grocery list + pantry memory.</p>
          <p class="coming-desc">
            Never forget what you have. Never forget what you need. PantryBaby gives you a single,
            always-up-to-date view of your pantry inventory and shopping list, so you can stop
            doing that mental inventory check every time you're at the store.
          </p>

          <!-- Notify CTA -->
          <div class="notify-section">
            <h2 class="notify-heading">Get notified at launch.</h2>
            <p class="notify-sub">No spam. Just a single email when PantryBaby is available.</p>
            <GlassCard padding="md">
              <div class="form-placeholder-inner">
                <span class="form-placeholder-icon">📬</span>
                <div>
                  <p class="form-placeholder-label">Email signup coming soon</p>
                  <p class="form-placeholder-note">
                    We'll be setting up our notification list shortly.<br />
                    In the meantime, send us a note at <a href="mailto:support@babyblocks.io">support@babyblocks.io</a> to be added manually.
                  </p>
                </div>
              </div>
            </GlassCard>
          </div>
        </div>

        <div class="coming-visual" aria-hidden="true">
          <div class="pantry-mock glass">
            <div class="mock-header">
              <span class="mock-app-icon">🥗</span>
              <span class="mock-app-name">PantryBaby</span>
            </div>
            <div class="mock-status-row">
              <div class="mock-stat">
                <span class="mock-stat-val">12</span>
                <span class="mock-stat-label">On list</span>
              </div>
              <div class="mock-stat">
                <span class="mock-stat-val status-low">8</span>
                <span class="mock-stat-label">Running low</span>
              </div>
              <div class="mock-stat">
                <span class="mock-stat-val status-out">3</span>
                <span class="mock-stat-label">Out of stock</span>
              </div>
            </div>
            <div class="mock-items">
              <div class="mock-item">
                <span class="mock-item-dot dot-low"></span>
                <span>Whole milk</span>
                <span class="mock-item-loc">Refrigerator</span>
              </div>
              <div class="mock-item">
                <span class="mock-item-dot dot-out"></span>
                <span>Pasta</span>
                <span class="mock-item-loc">Pantry</span>
              </div>
              <div class="mock-item">
                <span class="mock-item-dot dot-ok"></span>
                <span>Olive oil</span>
                <span class="mock-item-loc">Kitchen</span>
              </div>
              <div class="mock-item">
                <span class="mock-item-dot dot-low"></span>
                <span>Coffee</span>
                <span class="mock-item-loc">Pantry</span>
              </div>
              <div class="mock-item">
                <span class="mock-item-dot dot-out"></span>
                <span>Paper towels</span>
                <span class="mock-item-loc">Utilities</span>
              </div>
            </div>
          </div>
        </div>
      </div>
    </div>
  </section>

  <!-- What's coming -->
  <section class="whats-coming section-sm">
    <div class="container">
      <div class="section-header centered">
        <span class="eyebrow">What to expect</span>
        <h2>Built for real kitchens.</h2>
        <p>PantryBaby tracks your inventory across 14 home storage areas, helps you build smarter shopping lists, and reduces the food you waste.</p>
      </div>

      <div class="coming-features">
        <GlassCard glow>
          <div class="cf-item">
            <div class="cf-icon">📦</div>
            <h3>Pantry inventory</h3>
            <p>Track every item in your kitchen, pantry, fridge, freezer, and more with In Stock / Low / Out status at a glance. Expiration date tracking and alerts included.</p>
          </div>
        </GlassCard>

        <GlassCard glow>
          <div class="cf-item">
            <div class="cf-icon">🛒</div>
            <h3>Smart shopping lists</h3>
            <p>Build a list manually or let PantryBaby generate one from your low-stock and out-of-stock items. Per-item store preferences included.</p>
          </div>
        </GlassCard>

        <GlassCard glow>
          <div class="cf-item">
            <div class="cf-icon">🏪</div>
            <h3>Store-sorted shopping</h3>
            <p>Map aisles as you shop, and your list auto-sorts by aisle next time. Shop faster, backtrack less. (Premium feature.)</p>
          </div>
        </GlassCard>

        <GlassCard glow>
          <div class="cf-item">
            <div class="cf-icon">🔄</div>
            <h3>Recurring items</h3>
            <p>Set weekly milk and monthly cleaning supplies to auto-add to your list on schedule. Never forget the basics again.</p>
          </div>
        </GlassCard>

        <GlassCard glow>
          <div class="cf-item">
            <div class="cf-icon">🌍</div>
            <h3>18-region store support</h3>
            <p>Pre-loaded with region-specific store lists for 18 regions worldwide, from the UAE to the USA to Australia. Local shopping, simplified.</p>
          </div>
        </GlassCard>

        <GlassCard glow>
          <div class="cf-item">
            <div class="cf-icon">🧠</div>
            <h3>Smart suggestions</h3>
            <p>Based on your purchase history, PantryBaby notices when you're overdue for something you usually buy and adds it to your list automatically. (Premium feature.)</p>
          </div>
        </GlassCard>
      </div>
    </div>
  </section>

  <!-- BudgetBaby link -->
  <section class="bb-cta section-sm">
    <div class="container-sm">
      <GlassCard accent padding="lg">
        <div class="bb-cta-inner">
          <div>
            <p class="bb-cta-label">Available now</p>
            <h2>Looking for the budgeting app?</h2>
            <p>BudgetBaby, the BabyBlocks flagship, is available on the App Store today.</p>
            <a href="/budgetbaby" class="btn btn-primary" style="margin-top: var(--space-4);">
              Explore BudgetBaby →
            </a>
          </div>
          <div class="bb-icon" aria-hidden="true">💰</div>
        </div>
      </GlassCard>
    </div>
  </section>
</LayoutPantry>

<style>
  .coming-hero {
    padding-top: calc(var(--space-20) + var(--space-8));
  }

  .coming-inner {
    display: grid;
    grid-template-columns: 1fr 360px;
    gap: var(--space-16);
    align-items: center;
  }

  .coming-copy {
    display: flex;
    flex-direction: column;
    gap: var(--space-6);
  }

  .coming-copy h1 {
    font-size: clamp(var(--text-5xl), 8vw, var(--text-7xl));
    letter-spacing: -0.03em;
    line-height: 0.95;
    background: linear-gradient(135deg, #4A7B6E, #3D9970, #6AAF96);
    -webkit-background-clip: text;
    -webkit-text-fill-color: transparent;
    background-clip: text;
  }

  .coming-tagline {
    font-size: var(--text-2xl);
    font-weight: var(--weight-semibold);
    color: var(--text-primary) !important;
    margin: 0 !important;
  }

  .coming-desc {
    font-size: var(--text-lg);
    color: var(--text-secondary);
    max-width: 50ch;
  }

  /* Notify section */
  .notify-section { display: flex; flex-direction: column; gap: var(--space-3); }

  .notify-heading {
    font-size: var(--text-xl);
    font-weight: var(--weight-semibold);
  }

  .notify-sub {
    font-size: var(--text-sm);
    color: var(--text-muted);
    margin: 0 !important;
  }

  .form-placeholder-inner {
    display: flex;
    gap: var(--space-4);
    align-items: flex-start;
  }

  .form-placeholder-icon { font-size: 1.8rem; line-height: 1; flex-shrink: 0; }

  .form-placeholder-label {
    font-size: var(--text-sm);
    font-weight: var(--weight-semibold);
    color: var(--text-primary) !important;
    margin-bottom: var(--space-2) !important;
  }

  .form-placeholder-note {
    font-size: var(--text-xs) !important;
    color: var(--text-muted) !important;
    line-height: var(--leading-relaxed) !important;
    margin: 0 !important;
  }

  /* Pantry mock */
  .pantry-mock {
    padding: var(--space-6);
    background: rgba(255, 255, 255, 0.75) !important;
    border-color: rgba(74, 123, 110, 0.2) !important;
    box-shadow: 0 0 40px rgba(74, 123, 110, 0.1), var(--shadow-xl);
    display: flex;
    flex-direction: column;
    gap: var(--space-4);
  }

  .mock-header {
    display: flex;
    align-items: center;
    gap: var(--space-2);
    font-size: var(--text-base);
    font-weight: var(--weight-semibold);
    color: var(--text-primary);
  }

  .mock-app-icon { font-size: 1.3rem; }

  .mock-status-row {
    display: grid;
    grid-template-columns: repeat(3, 1fr);
    gap: var(--space-3);
    padding: var(--space-3);
    background: rgba(0,0,0,0.03);
    border-radius: var(--radius-md);
    border: 1px solid var(--glass-border);
  }

  .mock-stat {
    display: flex;
    flex-direction: column;
    align-items: center;
    gap: var(--space-1);
  }

  .mock-stat-val {
    font-size: var(--text-2xl);
    font-weight: 800;
    color: var(--text-primary);
    line-height: 1;
  }

  .mock-stat-val.status-low { color: var(--yellow); }
  .mock-stat-val.status-out { color: var(--red); }

  .mock-stat-label {
    font-size: var(--text-xs);
    color: var(--text-muted);
    text-align: center;
  }

  .mock-items {
    display: flex;
    flex-direction: column;
    gap: var(--space-2);
    border-top: 1px solid var(--glass-border);
    padding-top: var(--space-3);
  }

  .mock-item {
    display: flex;
    align-items: center;
    gap: var(--space-3);
    font-size: var(--text-sm);
    color: var(--text-secondary);
  }

  .mock-item-dot {
    width: 8px; height: 8px;
    border-radius: 50%;
    flex-shrink: 0;
  }

  .dot-ok  { background: var(--green); }
  .dot-low { background: var(--yellow); }
  .dot-out { background: var(--red); }

  .mock-item-loc {
    margin-left: auto;
    font-size: var(--text-xs);
    color: var(--text-faint);
  }

  /* Coming features */
  .coming-features {
    display: grid;
    grid-template-columns: repeat(3, 1fr);
    gap: var(--space-4);
  }

  .cf-item {
    display: flex;
    flex-direction: column;
    gap: var(--space-3);
  }

  .cf-icon { font-size: 2rem; line-height: 1; }

  .cf-item h3 { font-size: var(--text-lg); }

  .cf-item p {
    font-size: var(--text-sm);
    color: var(--text-secondary);
    line-height: var(--leading-relaxed);
  }

  /* BB CTA */
  .bb-cta-inner {
    display: flex;
    justify-content: space-between;
    align-items: center;
    gap: var(--space-8);
  }

  .bb-cta-label {
    font-size: var(--text-xs);
    font-weight: var(--weight-semibold);
    letter-spacing: 0.1em;
    text-transform: uppercase;
    color: var(--accent);
    margin-bottom: var(--space-2) !important;
  }

  .bb-cta-inner h2 { font-size: var(--text-2xl); margin-bottom: var(--space-2); }
  .bb-cta-inner > div > p { font-size: var(--text-sm); color: var(--text-secondary); margin: 0; }

  .bb-icon { font-size: 4rem; line-height: 1; flex-shrink: 0; opacity: 0.5; }

  @media (max-width: 900px) {
    .coming-inner { grid-template-columns: 1fr; }
    .coming-visual { order: -1; max-width: 340px; }
    .coming-features { grid-template-columns: repeat(2, 1fr); }
    .bb-cta-inner { flex-direction: column; }
    .bb-icon { display: none; }
  }

  @media (max-width: 600px) {
    .coming-features { grid-template-columns: 1fr; }
  }
</style>
